visited and time spent on each page"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Click patterns and navigation behavior"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Device identifiers"}]]}],["$","h3",null,{"children":"1.4 Cookies and Tracking Technologies"}],["$","p",null,{"children":["We use cookies, web beacons, and similar technologies to enhance your experience, analyze usage patterns, and deliver relevant content. For detailed information, please refer to our"," ",["$","a",null,{"href":"/policies/cookies","className":"text-blue-600 hover:underline","children":"Cookie Policy"}],"."]}],["$","h2",null,{"children":"2. How We Use Your Information"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"We use the information we collect for the following purposes:"}],["$","ul",null,{"children":[["$","li",null,{"children":"Processing and fulfilling your orders"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Communicating with you about your account, orders, and inquiries"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Providing customer support"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Improving our Site, products, and services"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Personalizing your experience on the Site"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Sending transactional emails (order confirmations, shipping updates)"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Detecting and preventing fraud and unauthorized access"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Complying with legal obligations"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Conducting analytics and market research"}]]}],["$","h2",null,{"children":"3. Third-Party Sharing"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"We do not sell your personal information to third parties. We may share your information with the following categories of service providers who assist us in operating the Site and conducting our business:"}],["$","ul",null,{"children":[["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"Payment processors:"}]," To securely process your transactions (e.g., Stripe, Square)."]}],["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"Shipping carriers:"}]," To 